<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Document</title>
</head>
<style>
        h2 {
            text-align: center;
            text-decoration: underline #FF7A3D;
            margin: 20px;
            }

            h2:hover,
            h2.active {
            color: #000000;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        /* Experience Section */
        .section {
            padding: 5rem 5%;
        }
        
        .section-title {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
        }
        
        .section-title h2 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }
        
        .section-title p {
            color: #636e72;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .timeline {
            position: relative;
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 2rem 0;
        }
        
        .timeline::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            width: 6px;
            background-color: #ff7a3d80;
            top: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            left: 50%;
            margin-left: -3px;
            border-radius: 10px;
        }
        
        .timeline-item {
            padding: 10px 40px;
            position: relative;
            width: 50%;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        .timeline-item::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            width: 25px;
            height: 25px;
            right: -12px;
            background-color: white;
            border: 4px solid #ff7a3d80;
            top: 15px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            z-index: 1;
        }
        
        .left {
            left: 0;
        }
        
        .right {
            left: 50%;
        }
        
        .right::after {
            left: -12px;
        }
        
        .timeline-content {
            padding: 20px 30px;
            background-color: white;
            position: relative;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
        }
        
        .timeline-content h3 {
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
            color: #6c5ce7;
        }
        
        .timeline-content h4 {
            font-size: 1rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            color: #fd79a8;
        }
        
        .timeline-content p {
            color: #636e72;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        
        .timeline-date {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #2d3436;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 0.3rem 0.8rem;
            background-color: #f5f6fa;
            border-radius: 50px;
        }

        
        /* Responsive Styles */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .timeline::after {
                left: 8px;
                display: none;
            }

            .timeline-item {
                width: 100%;
                padding-left: 5px;
                padding-right: 5px;
                margin-bottom: 2rem;
            }

            .timeline-item::after {
                left: 0;
                right: auto;
                display: none;
            }

            .left,
            .right {
                left: 0;
            }

            .right::after {
                left: 0;
            }

            .timeline-content {
                padding: 20px;
            }

            .section-title h2 {
                font-size: 2rem;
            }

            .section {
                padding: 3rem 2%;
            }
        }
        
</style>
<body>
        <!-- Experience Section -->
        <section class="section" id="experience">
            <div class="section-title">
                <h2>My Work Experience</h2>
                <p>Here's a timeline of my professional journey.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="timeline">
                <div class="timeline-item left fade-in">
                    <div class="timeline-content">
                        <span class="timeline-date">May 2024 - Jul 2024</span>
                        <h3>Web Development Intern</h3>
                        <h4>Slash Mark IT Solutions (OPC) Pvt. Ltd</h4>
                        <p>Dynamic web applications using JavaScript, PHP, Node.js, and PhpMyAdmin. Collaborated on backend development, database management, and API integration. 
                            Gained hands-on experience in full-stack development within an AICTE-approved internship program.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="timeline-item right fade-in" style="animation-delay: 0.2s;">
                    <div class="timeline-content">
                        <span class="timeline-date">Sep 2024 - Present</span>
                        <h3>Technical Team Member</h3>
                        <h4>Google Developer Student Clubs (GDSC)</h4>
                        <p>Actively contributing to technical projects and events focused on web development, cloud, and 
                            open-source technologies. Collaborating with cross-functional teams to build innovative solutions,
                             mentor peers, and support technical initiatives within the GDSC community.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="timeline-item left fade-in" style="animation-delay: 0.4s;">
                    <div class="timeline-content">
                        <span class="timeline-date">Nov 2022 - Present</span>
                        <h3>Educational Content Creator</h3>
                        <h4>Helper YT</h4>
                        <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Duis lacus nunc, posuere in justo vulputate, bibendum sodales</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
</body>
</html>
